The second round of group games in the Champions League, will be played this midweek around Europe. Former champions Real Madrid host Club Brugge, after losing 3-0 to PSG in their first fixture. Tottenham Hotspur welcome Bayern Munich, while PSG travel to Galatasaray. Atletico Madrid are away to Lokomotiv Moscow and Juventus host Bayer Levekusen. GROUP A
17:55 Real Madrid vs Club Brugge
20:00 Galatasaray vs Paris Saint-Germain GROUP B
20:00 FK Crvena Zvezda vs Olympiacos
20:00 Tottenham Hotspur vs FC Bayern München GROUP C
17:55 Atalanta vs Shakhtar Donetsk
20:00 Manchester City vs Dinamo Zagreb GROUP D
20:00 Juventus vs Bayer Leverkusen
